Date: Thu, 27 May 2021 14:41:34 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 4/8] arm: dts: imx7d-colibri-emmc: Enable Display interfaces

Toradex Easy Installer does not support dedicated colibri-imx7-emmc
target. Overlays can't be clearly applied to NAND device tree.

Enable lcdif, backlight and panel-dpi interfaces by default.

Related-to: TEI-746
Signed-off-by: Denys Drozdov <denys.drozdov@toradex.com>
---
 arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d-colibri-emmc.dtsi | 12 ++++++++++++
 1 file changed, 12 insertions(+)

diff --git a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d-colibri-emmc.dtsi b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d-colibri-emmc.dtsi
index 9b5621cf9f32..3258bd01fc32 100644
--- a/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d-colibri-emmc.dtsi
+++ b/arch/arm/boot/dts/imx7d-colibri-emmc.dtsi
@@ -70,3 +70,15 @@ &usbotg2 {
 &usdhc3 {
 	status = "okay";
 };
+
+&backlight {
+	status = "okay";
+};
+
+&lcdif {
+	status = "okay";
+};
+
+&panel_dpi {
+	status = "okay";
+};
